Add up all the dependency distances: 1 + 2 + 3 + 2 + 3 + 1 + 2 + 4 + 1 + 2 + 1 + 1 + 2 + 1 + 3 + 2 + 1 + 2 + 3 + 1 + 2 + 1 + 1 + 4 + 1 + 1 + 1 + 2 (since we ignore the last token) = 52

There are 27 tokens in the sentence excluding the punctuation mark at the end. However, 2 tokens don't have heads ('.' and it is excluded and a token isn't head of others and also all the dependency distances aren't added with one more than expected)    Instead of using 27 for total tokens with heads, use 27-1=26.

Calculate the average dependency distance:
Average dependency distance = 52 / 26
